rows.label: tev001092_MSG0001
rows.name: Oh... [ST:playername ]. Hello.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0002
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire Generally

rows.label: tev001092_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Phog how his day's going.

rows.label: tev001092_JNK0020
rows.name: Inquire Specifically

rows.label: tev001092_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Phog if he likes cats.

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0006
rows.name:
My day? It's fine, thank you. As you can see,
I'm having a staring contest with a cat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0007
rows.name:
If I were to look away for even a moment,
I know it would leap at me and slash my face
repeatedly with its evil, evil claws.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0008
rows.name: Me? No. Not at all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0009
rows.name: Actually, I despise the wretched creatures.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0010
rows.name: But they started it. They're always cruel to me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0011
rows.name:
For example, if I were to turn my gaze from this one
for even a moment, I know it would leap at me and
slash my face repeatedly with its evil, evil claws.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0012
rows.name:
Back on Earth, the common house cat, or Felis catus,
was ever a nemesis of mine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0013
rows.name:
I'd hoped things would be different here. After all,
the Ma-non and Nopon have different languages,
but for some reason we all understand each other.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0014
rows.name:
So with that in mind, I was trying to establish a form
of meaningful communication with the local cats.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0015
rows.name:
It doesn't really seem to be working out, however.
Why do you think cats and I aren't capable of
understanding each other?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_JNK0030
rows.name: Speculate

rows.label: tev001092_SEL0031
rows.name: Guess that a cat's meow doesn't contain words.

rows.label: tev001092_JNK0040
rows.name: Encourage

rows.label: tev001092_SEL0041
rows.name:
Say that Phog may meet a cat
he can understand one day.

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0016
rows.name: That...is sound reasoning.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0017
rows.name:
Such a theory assumes that a cat's meowing is not
actually a language at all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0018
rows.name:
Which means that cats and I may be doomed to an
eternally adversarial relationship.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0019
rows.name: I suppose that's a possibility...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0020
rows.name:
I certainly haven't conducted my experiment on all of
the cats here on Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0021
rows.name:
One day I may indeed meet a cat who has no interest
in using my face for a scratching post.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001092_MSG0022
rows.name:
I will hold that hope in my heart throughout my
remaining years on this planet.[ST:wait ]
